<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.1">
<l>nāma māyira mētta niṉṟa nārāyaṇā naraṉē yuṉṉai</l>
<l>māmi taṉmaka ṉākap peṟṟā lemakku vātai tavirumē</l>
<l>kāmaṉ pōtaru kāla meṉṟupaṅ kuṉināḷ kaṭaipā rittōn</l>
<l>tīmai ceyyuñ cirītarā veṅkaḷ ciṟṟil vantu citaiyēlē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Nārāyaṇa who have remained [being] praised [by means of] a thousand names! O Nara!</l>
<l>If [our] aunt (Yaśodā) obtains You as [her] son, can we avoid torment?</l>
<l>Thinking that it is time for Kāma’s arrival, we worshipped with flowers [his] path</l>
<l rend="indent">on Paṅkuṉi days.</l>
<l>O Sridhara who do mischief! Do not come and trample down our small [sand] house!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
